title: How Does Each Team Get to the Super Bowl?
description:
Kevin and Nora go through each matchup of the Super Wild-Card Weekend and discuss potential ways for each team to reach the Super Bowl. 

Host: Kevin Clark and Nora Princiotti 
Associate Producer: Stefan Anderson
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
